Company 

Home
Company















Empowering service providers
We empower service providers to monetize and optimize their networks, enterprises to enhance productivity and consumers to enjoy an always-on digital lifestyle. Our advanced DPI-based broadband solutions leverage network intelligence to analyze, protect, improve and monetize the user experience over mobile, fixed and cloud assets.
Technology, know-how and collaboration
Our unique blend of innovative technology, proven know-how and collaborative approach to industry standards and partnerships enables service providers worldwide to elevate their role in the digital experience ecosystem and to open the door to a wealth of new business opportunities. 





Value-added solutions with high-performance platforms
Our integrated high-performance platforms deliver analytics, traffic management, video caching and optimization, policy and charging and service enablement capabilities to allow service providers to increase revenue, reduce costs, improve customer loyalty and reduce churn. For enterprises and cloud service providers, we improve application visibility, control and performance, enhance security and ensure high user quality of experience. 






