Products















Intelligent broadband solutions for digital lifestyles
We are a leading global provider of intelligent broadband solutions that put mobile, fixed and enterprise networks at the center of digital services. Our rich portfolio of high-performance platforms, integrated services, and insightful analytics empower network operators to shape the digital experience and capitalize on the network traffic they generate.





Our products create real value for network operators
Our products utilize open architecture and standard interfaces allow us to collaborate with leading solution providers and a growing cadre of service vendors in the digital ecosystem, including SDN/NFV environments. Our products and solutions are backed by a global support organization with technical experts providing 24/7 coverage around the world. Consequently, we are able to deliver tangible results and create real value for our customers around the world.






Spotlight










Service Gateway Tera
Our high-performance DPI-based platform is built to power the deployment of digital lifestyle services in fixed and mobile data networks. Read more.










Virtual TDF
Our virtual Traffic Detection Function (vTDF) technology eliminates massive investments in installation, integration, updating and maintenance. The result is lower costs and real data monetization through increased revenues. Read more.










ClearSee Analytics
By capturing a rich variety of contextual statistics and facilitating actionable analytics, ClearSee Data Source enables you to make more informed business decisions that drive customer satisfaction and revenue generation. Read more.






Learn More





Analytics  Turn big data into usable data that drives customer satisfaction and service profitability. Read More »    


Security  Ensure service integrity for your network and subscribers by protecting against DDoS and zero-day attacks, worms, zombies and spambots. Read More »    


Optimization 
Optimize QoE for every user and application, even during peak usage times.
Read More »    


Service Integration  Power service deployment of networks on the path to software-defined networking and cloud-based network services using our high performance DPI-based platform. Read More »    


Policy and Charging  Manage your subscribers with policies and orchestrate usage-based and application-based charging models using our Subscriber Management platform. Read More »    


Platforms 
